            "title": "Ecological drivers of selection for remnant forest habitats by an insectivorous bat in a tropical, human-modified landscape",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Harish",
                    "lastName": "Prakash"
                },
                {
