            "title": "HEMATOLOGICAL PROFILE OF THREE SPECIES OF Hipposideros spp. (HIPPOSIDERIDAE) AS AN ADAPTATION IN CAVE HABITAT, IN GUNUNG SEWU GEOPARK AREA, INDONESIA",
            "creators": [
