            "title": "Differences between populations of Spinturnix myoti (Acari: Mesostigmata) in breeding and non-breeding colonies of Myotis myotis (Chiroptera) in central Europe: the effect of roost type",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Tomasz",
                    "lastName": "Postawa"
                },
